text:
**Example (JavaScript):**
```javascript
// Function expects an object with a 'quack' method
function makeSound(duck) {
  duck.quack(); 
}

class Duck {
  quack() { console.log("Quack!"); }
}

class Robot {
  // Not a Duck class, but has the quack method
  quack() { console.log("Beep-Quack!"); }
}

makeSound(new Duck());    // Works
makeSound(new Robot());   // Works (Duck Typing!)
```

